		<title xml:space="preserve"><![CDATA[After-School Roleplay]]></title>
		<content type="html" xml:space="preserve" xml:base="https://www.burgershot.gg/showthread.php?tid=1717"><![CDATA[<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive;" class="mycode_font">Inceputul </span></span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Ca peste tot , inceputul e greu cand vine vorba de un nou server de samp.Iti pui tot felul de intrebari de genul : E de durata ? Oare se merita ? si multe altele .Nu am sa-ti raspund la aceasta intrebare .Tu decizi ! Nu ai nimic de pierdut .Cert este ca incercam sa lucram cat mai profesionist posibil pentru a va aduce un mod de joc cat mai placut .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Modul de joc este Roleplay Light .Ce inseamna asta ? Inseamna ca jucatorii nu sunt concentrati doar pe roleplay si in general , ei se pot bucura de alte aspecte ale jocului .Asta nu inseamna ca ei au dreptul sa evite anumite situatii unde chiar necesita roleplay cum se cuvine .De asemenea pentru a face parte dintr-o factiune / guvern sau gang sau chiar sa devii leader unuia , esti obligat sa ai cunostinte vaste despre asta pentru ca vei fi supus unor teste , unde concurenta va fi foarte mare .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Economia este una scazuta , unde face jocul cat mai realist .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acomodarea cu sistemele de business</span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Server-ul nostru dispune de o larga serie de business-uri , precum :</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Magazine publicitare - unde jucatorii pot intra , plasand un anunt prioritar care va fi afisat tuturor jucatorilor online pe server , platind o anumita suma de bani .Important de spus , este ca oricine poate detine un magazin publicitar , iar banii incasati din anunturi se duc in seiful afacerii la care accesul il are doar proprietarul acestuia .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Magazinul general ( sau bine cunoscutul 24/7) - Tastand comanda /buy , ti se va deschide un dialog cu o varietate de produse ce iti vor fi de folos in joc .Bineinteles acestea costa bani , deci asigura-te ca ai suficienti bani in cont .Toti banii incasati de catre un magazin general se vor duce in seiful acestuia , si cum bine stiti doar proprietarul are acces la acesta .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Magazinul de arme - cei mai multi jucatori , iubesc acest timp de afacere .In acest tip de afacere , veti gasi doar armele legale pe server-ul nostru .Cele ilegale le puteti procura de la Dealeri de arme .De asemenea acest tip de afacere poate fi cumparat de orice jucator si cum bine v-am obisnuit toti banii incasati in urma vanzarilor , se duc in seiful afacerii .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Avem si alte tipuri de afaceri , cel mai bine alatura-te si tu comunitatii noastre si descopera chiar TU ! Multe dintre business-uri pot fi folosite ca sediu a gang-urilor ca exemplu : Night Club .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Important: Poti detine cate business-uri doresti .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acomodarea cu sistemul de case </span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Aici nu sunt prea multe de zis .Fiecare dintre noi isi doreste una pentru diferite motive precum : ai un gang sau iti doresti sa infiintezi unul si nu ai un sediu , ascunderea drogurilor / armelor sau pur si simplu sa ai un loc unde sa dormi .Casele pot fi inchiriate , daca proprietarul este de acord cu asta .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Daca sunteti un dealer de droguri , si casa dumneavoastra a fost desconspirata ca fiind un laborator de droguri , va puteti trezi cu perchezitii , marfa confiscata si arestarea dumneavoastra .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font"> Important : Poti detine cate case doresti </span></span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]    Acomodarea cu factiunile si gang-urile </span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Fiind membru unei factiuni , este cel mai interesant si frumos lucru avand numeroase beneficii precum : arme gratis , skin-uri , nume colorat in TAB , salarii si multe altele .Dar nu uita ca membru sau leader ai si responsabilitati .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Factiunile server-ului nostru sunt :  L.S.P.D , F.B.I , Los Santos Fire &amp; Medical Department , Hitman Agency , Government , San Andreas News .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]LSFMD - membrii acestei factiuni sunt platiti de fiecare data cand duce un pacient la spital , fiindca acesta a ajuns intr-o stare critica .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]LSPD - este cea mai mare factiune patruland pentru linistea orasului .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]FBI - este o organizatie sub acoperire care pot deschide dosare penale .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Government - ca angajat in guvern , esti responsabil pentru a proteja presedintele , respectand sarcinile date de acesta si a te asigura de buna starea cetatenilor .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]San Andreas News - Este factiunea care transmite stiri / anunturi / live-uri pentru a informa cetatenii despre tot ce se intampla in oras .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Hitman Agency - este o factiune bine cunoscuta de jucatori si DAW de asemenea .Ca hitman , tu poti sa omori oameni care sunt sub contract primind jumatate din suma la finalizarea lui .Suma maxima pentru care poti pune contract este de 50.000 &#36; .Pentru a evita abuzurile , liderii acestei factiuni vor fi in mare parte a timpului adminii .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Gang-urile - pot fi create de catre anumiti admini responsabili pe latura aceasta . Cei ce vor sa infiinteze un gang , este nevoit sa aplice pe forum pentru acest lucru ,completand un formular .Va trebui sa asteptati pentru analizarea lui si aprobarea / respingerea lui .Mai multe informatii gasiti in sectiunea corespunzatoare pe forum </span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color">Acomodarea cu factiunea Universitate<br />
</span><br />
<div style="text-align: left;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color">O noua factiune isi face prezenta pe server-ul nostru si anume Universitatea , unde fiecare jucator ce doreste sa faca parte din politie sau oricare factiune (excluzand gangurile) ca lider sau simplu membru ,va trebui sa ia parte la cursuri si examene .Ce fel de cursuri ?In general ,jucatorii vor invata sa faca roleplay dar si cum sa se comporte ca un membru intr-o factiune .</span></div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Comenzile din chat</span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Aceste comenzi nu sunt greu de retinut , dar e frustrant cand esti incepator .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/me (emotii , trairi ori actiuni)</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/do (exprima o actiune , mai mult o confirmare a /me)</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/b - este folosit pentru OOC (local chat)</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/w - folosit pentru OOC sau IC  sa soptesti unui jucator care e in apropierea ta .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/newb - destinat tuturor jucatorilor in special celor noi care au intrebari referitoare la script .Acest tip de chat este doar pentru Q/A .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/f - este comanda pentru family chat si este folosita in cazuri OOC</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/pr - Personal radio chat .Iti poti cumpara unul din magazinul general si iti poti seta propria frecventa si sa vorbesti cu alti jucatori pe care ii inviti pe canalul tau .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/r - chat pentru departamente .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/d chat pentru toate departamentele</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/sms sau /t pentru a trimite mesaj cuiva </span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]/number - pentru a afla numarul de telefon cuiva / trebuie sa cumperi o carte de telefon si sa detii un telefon </span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acomodarea cu sistemul de vehicule</span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acest sistem de vehicule este unul destul de simplu .Pentru a mentine propria masina in siguranta ai nevoie de o incuietoare .Asta o face mai safe in fata hotilor .Acolo veti gasi doua tipuri de incuietori : Alarm lock - in care masina dumneavoastra va face beep cand cineva incearca sa intre in ea sau Industrial Lock  - tipul acestei incuietori nu va permite hotilor sa o sparga , daca aceasta e incuiata [ /lock ] .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Server-ul dispune de multiple dealership-uri , de la cele mai ietine , la cele mai scumpe .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acomodarea cu sistemul de drug smuggling / Drug dealer </span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Acest job este unul ilegal si banos , dar trebuie sa fii cu ochii in 4 dupa politisti .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Drug smuggling - la acest job , esti mai mult un caraus , unde esti trimis din punctul A in punctul B pentru a alimenta Crack House .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]Drug Dealer - Poti lua seminte de la drug house , doar daca aceasta are .Daca aceasta nu are seminte , va trebui sa muncesti ca drug smuggling ca sa alimentezi .Acest sistem este la comun .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font="Comic Sans MS", cursive]O data ce ai procurat semintele , poti merge sa le plantezi oriunde .De recomandat este sa le plantati in loc cat mai ferit de ochii lumii pentru ca acestea pot fi furate de alti jucatori .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font=Comic Sans MS, cursive]Acomodarea cu sistemul Double XP </span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font=Comic Sans MS, cursive]Acest sistem , da oportunitatea jucatorilor ca in timpul lucrului ( job-ului ) sa dobanditi de x2 mai mult skill points la joburi .Acesta se activeaza printr-o simpla modificare in script si nu in joc .De retinut , faptul ca el va fi activat doar la ocazii pe o perioada limitata de timp .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font=Comic Sans MS, cursive]Anuntul se va face cu o saptamana inainte .</span>[/font]</span></span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font">[font=Comic Sans MS, cursive]Despre Payday</span>[/font]</span></span></div>
<span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';" class="mycode_font"><span style="color: #444444;" class="mycode_color">[font=Comic Sans MS, cursive]Payday-ul se acorda la fiecare ora fixa xx:00 .Payday-ul se anunta atat in chat cat si pe ecran.Atunci , aveti la dispozitie 5 minute sa tastati comanda /signcheck urmata de un dialog cu cifre random date sa le adaugati  .O data semnat check-ul , primiti payday-ul .Daca cele 5 minute s-au scurs si incercati sa dati /signcheck , aceasta nu va functiona si va trebui sa asteptati pana la urmatorul payday .</span></span>[/font]</span>]]></content>
